      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Your fervent mind toward me; so that I rejoiced the more:",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " your earnest desire to give me satisfaction, and yield obedience to my admonitions, or to maintain and defend my honour and reputation against such as had impeached and wounded it; these things much augmented my rejoicing in and over you. Nothing so much rejoiceth the heart of a conscientious, faithful minister of Christ, as to see his people’s obedience to the doctrine of the gospel, which he is an instrument to communicate to them. ",
        "children": []
