        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "toward me",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "]) Because the Corinthians showed a “fervent mind,” Paul was relieved from the exercise of that fervour.—",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ὥστε με μᾶλλον",
