        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "so that I rather",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " [“the more”]) An imperceptible transition. I had not so much consolation, as joy: joy is ",
